# 🎮 Spirit Esports

A full-stack esports web application built with React and Node.js, supporting authentication, API integration, and SQL-based data persistence. Deployed using Vercel.

------------

## 📁 Project Structure
Spirit Esports/
├── Client/ # Frontend (React)
├── Server/ # Backend (Node.js, Express, MySQL)
├── .gitignore
├── README.md

------------

## 🚀 Tech Stack

| Layer        | Tech                        |
|--------------|-----------------------------|
| Frontend     | HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React.js |
| Backend      | Node.js, Express.js         |
| Database     | MySQL                       |
| Auth         | JWT                         |
| API Calls    | Axios                       |
| Deployment   | Vercel (Frontend + Backend) |

------------

## 🛠️ Setup Instructions

1. Clone the Repository

git clone
cd spirit-esports

2. 📦 Install Dependencies

    Frontend (Client):
    cd Client
    npm install

    Backend (Server):
    cd ../Server
    npm install

3. ⚙️ Environment Variables
Copy the env.example to .env

4. 🧪 Running the App Locally

Start Backend:

cd Server
npm start

Start Frontend:
Open a new terminal:

cd Client
npm start

Frontend: http://localhost:3000
Backend: http://localhost:5000

